{"tid":1977910,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"理髮師死罪","createTime":"2020-04-18T10:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T15:19:48.000Z","uid":312758,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d16925025857c191107d3a52fc5cf8765d008f","tid":1977910,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老味</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日去剪個頭髮(洗剪吹)<br />\n洗:你洗撚濕埋我件衫，算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吹:對住同一個位一直吹，頭皮都就黎燶，算我忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你全家</span></span>，剪完一次洗撚完頭吹埋，你又再落刀。玩鳩我啊?我要三寶就係唔想成身頭髮碎，完場前再剪兩野又唔洗多次。仆你個街，哥幾舊水當買個教訓，食屎啦你個垃圾飛髮佬!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658ef7e26a6ad1dd2bf0b0c6137f2c223058cd13","tid":1977910,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"Ok網路公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3bc351311ab666dde80ab4a96f73a9265a0dd5","tid":1977910,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你去咗邊間，介紹嚟聽吓。等我列入黑名單，不過我大多數都去10分鐘剪頭髮，因為次次去salon 嫌好慢，自己返去洗頭焗油仲平過係salon整。<br />\n<br />\n我宜家男朋友都唔出去剪，本身佢去開10分鐘個啲，但話怕污糟，宜家叫我幫佢修剪，如果唔係要求太大變化，可以叫你女朋友偷薄，修短就好了。"},{"pid":"06a4bd4ef86c75eefc5a304a2dd353ebb012e861","tid":1977910,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d16925025857c191107d3a52fc5cf8765d008f","tid":1977910,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老味</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日去剪個頭髮(洗剪吹)<br />\n洗:你洗撚濕埋我件衫，算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吹:對住同一個位一直吹，頭皮都就黎燶，算我忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你全家</span></span>，剪完一次洗撚完頭吹埋，你又再落刀。玩鳩我啊?我要三寶就係唔想成身頭髮碎，完場前再剪兩野又唔洗多次。仆你個街，哥幾舊水當買個教訓，食屎啦你個垃圾飛髮佬!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"話我頭髮短留唔到馬尾，草平頭唔留得馬尾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}